AB  - This paper considers the disturbance specification ε = v − u of the stochastic frontier model. For v distributed zero-mean normal and u half normal or exponential, we evaluate the population correlation coefficients between u and three estimators of u, E(u|ε) and two linear estimators, for various values of the signal-to-noise ratio.
